title: Grateful Dead Live at Sun Dome on 1985-10-26
lineage: Master PCM > DAW (via SEKD Prodif) > Wav; Mastering by Dave Usborne: Izotope Ozone 5 Paragraphic EQ used for De-Emphasis Izotope RX Advanced Declick and Spectral Repair used manually to fix pops and digital artifacts. Editing done in Reaper V4.591/X64; Tracks cut in Audacity 2.0.5; Flac files created in Traders Little Helper
description:
Set 1

Gimme Some Lovin'-> Greatest Story Ever Told, Dupree's Diamond Blues, CC Rider, Stagger Lee, Me & My Uncle-> Big River, Big Railroad Blues, Looks Like Rain-> Don't Ease Me In

Set 2

China Cat Sunflower-> I Know You Rider, Women Are Smarter, He's Gone-> Don't Need Love-> Drums-> Comes A Time-> Throwing Stones-> Goin' Down The Road Feelin' Bad-> One More Saturday Night, E: Midnight Hour
